  <brief_title>Study With Rituximab, Cyclophosphamide, Doxorubicin Liposomal (Myocet®), Vincristine, Prednisone, (R-COMP) to Treat Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Study of Phase II With Rituximab, Cyclophosphamide, Doxorubicin Liposomal (Myocet ®), Vincristine, Prednisone, (R-COMP) in Non-Hodgkin's Lymphoma Diffuse Large B Cell in Cardiopathic Patients</official_title>
