  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter study phase II, open-label for cardiopathic patients affected by
      Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma diffuse large B cell CD20 + grade IIIb follicular. The purpose is to
      study the feasibility of R-COMP in this cohort of patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
